OL,5, Dozens of archaeological sites in      
OL,6, Afghanistan have been bulldozed to     
OL,7, allow systematic looting, according to 
OL,8, researchers at Chicago University.     
OL,10,FThey say their analysis of satellite   
OL,11,Fphotos provides the first definitive   
OL,12,Fphotographic evidence that looting     
OL,13,Fpatterns that began under the previous 
OL,14,Fgovernment have continued since the    
OL,15,FTaliban returned to power in 2021.     
OL,17,FAncient settlements dating back to the 
OL,18,FLate Bronze Age and Iron Age - some    
OL,19,Fearlier than 1000BC - are among those  
OL,20,Fthey say have been damaged.            
